Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.60,0:01:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要知道  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有时候就应该放着滑翔翼不用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,sometimes it's nice to hang up my hang glider
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.54,0:01:09.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,静静观赏云朵飘过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:09.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and just watch the clouds roll by
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.85,0:01:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.67,0:01:12.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还要放松
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:12.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And just relax
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.64,0:01:13.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:13.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.90,0:01:16.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放松
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:16.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,relax
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.92,0:01:19.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你知道那朵云像什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.92,0:01:19.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know what that cloud looks like?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.43,0:01:19.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:19.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.25,0:01:21.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一朵花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:21.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A flower
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.87,0:01:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里所有云都很像花  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They all look like flowers, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.80,0:01:24.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从来都是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:24.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all the time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.70,0:01:26.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.70,0:01:26.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They sure do
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.92,0:01:28.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,平常我都会跟你比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:28.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, normally I'd offer to race you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.80,0:01:30.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑到珊瑚崖上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.80,0:01:30.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the top of Coral Cliffs
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.29,0:01:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过这美景我一秒都不愿意错过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.29,0:01:31.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I don't want to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,miss out on a second of this beautiful beauty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.84,0:01:35.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:35.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me either
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.95,0:01:37.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁还会想一起比一比
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.95,0:01:37.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants to get all dirty anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.07,0:01:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.87,0:01:39.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那样还会流汗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:39.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and sweaty
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.80,0:01:43.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且咱俩心知肚明谁会先登顶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:43.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Besides, I think we know who'd get to the top first
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.47,0:01:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.71,0:01:46.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:46.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.92,0:01:49.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:49.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's funny, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.33,0:01:50.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚好像说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:50.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sounded like you said
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.50,0:01:52.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以捷足先登
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:52.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you could beat me in a climbing contest
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.01,0:01:54.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:54.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Course I can
Dialogue: 1,0:01:54.25,0:01:55.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:55.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.51,0:01:56.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:56.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.87,0:01:58.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为那标志表示你是坚果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:01:58.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought that meant you were nuts
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.40,0:01:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:01:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.22,0:02:01.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那标志表示我是天生攀岩好手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:01.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It means I'm a natural born climber
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.39,0:02:02.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是从陆地上来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:02.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm from the surface world
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.79,0:02:04.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想攀得一手好岩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:04.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and nothing prepares you for climbing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.38,0:02:06.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,成长环境最好还得是干燥的陆地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:06.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like growing up on good old dry land
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.60,0:02:08.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,陆什么地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:08.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Land-shmand
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.95,0:02:11.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手指力量才重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:11.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all about finger strength, baby
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.97,0:02:14.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在海底下最不缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:14.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if there's anything we've got plenty of down here
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.87,0:02:16.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是手指力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:16.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's finger strength
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.62,0:02:20.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢  手套小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:20.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you say to that, Miss Mittens?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.32,0:02:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经到半山腰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say I'm already halfway there
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不公平  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No fair, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.10,0:02:30.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你抢跑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:30.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got a head start
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊瑚就是这样一步步瓦解的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the way the coral crumbles
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.90,0:02:38.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:38.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did that on purpose
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.12,0:02:41.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  不过这次不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:41.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but this is a accident
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.81,0:02:46.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜你忘了带雨伞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:46.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too bad you forgot your umbrella
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没忘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.23,0:02:53.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在也该到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:53.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's about time you showed up
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.31,0:02:54.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你刚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:54.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you were
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.13,0:02:54.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:54.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saw you
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.96,0:02:55.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:55.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要复赛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:57.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want a rematch
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.06,0:03:01.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁第一个到蟹堡王谁就赢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:01.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First one to the Krusty Krab is the winner
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海底生物绝对不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't no way a sea critter
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.21,0:03:04.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑赢陆地生物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:04.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can run faster than a land critter
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.75,0:03:05.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在水下绝对行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:05.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can underwater
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.99,0:03:06.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:06.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.78,0:03:09.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,设计符合流体力学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:09.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hydrodynamically designed
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.65,0:03:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿着一身笨重的锡管还想赢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.65,0:03:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Think you can win a fair race in that clunky tin tube?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.57,0:03:14.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想问就先得落后我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:14.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask my be-hind?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.80,0:03:15.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:15.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.65,0:03:16.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少也得先赶上我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:16.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,if you can catch it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.92,0:03:19.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你意下如何  流体动力宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:19.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you say to that, Hydropants?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都已经
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I say, I'm already
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到半路了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,halfway there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.27,0:03:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到半路了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,halfway there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到半路了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:24.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,halfway there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.92,0:03:26.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到半路了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:26.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,halfway there
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你脸当我垫脚石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the face lift
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:35.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(490,456)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.47,0:03:39.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早就跟你说你没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:39.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, I told you you didn't have a
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这位陆地生物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ain't that just like a land creature
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.63,0:03:45.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害一位海底生物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:45.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to keep a sea creature
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,苦等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,waiting
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.98,0:03:51.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都说好了要复赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:51.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought y'all wanted a rematch
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.35,0:03:52.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:52.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.20,0:03:54.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且我跟你一样抢跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:54.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I took a head start like you did
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我那次只是在跟你开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just funnin' with ya that time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.77,0:03:58.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过看来你们海底生物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:58.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I guess all y'all underwater
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.31,0:03:59.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是用不着公平竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:03:59.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,don't have to play fair
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.62,0:04:02.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实  呼吸空气的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:02.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess we don't, air breather
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吸水的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Water sucker
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爬树的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tree climber
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.42,0:04:05.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住湾流的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:05.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gulf streamer
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.35,0:04:06.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放风筝的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:06.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kite flier
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.22,0:04:06.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃鱼饵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:06.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Chum chewer
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.15,0:04:10.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,收回你的话  你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:10.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take that back, you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不湿的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not-wet person
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想不出别的外号了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't even come up with another name
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.37,0:04:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,证据确凿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That proves it
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.70,0:04:19.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,证什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:19.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Proves what?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:19.77,0:04:22.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,陆地生物就是比海底生物强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:22.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That land critters are better than sea critters
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.77,0:04:23.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,强在哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:23.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better at what?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.65,0:04:26.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大概是样样都强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:26.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Durn near everything, I guess
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.12,0:04:28.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,套牛  吃派
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:28.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cattle ropin and pie eatin'
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.06,0:04:28.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有砍树
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:28.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and wood choppin'
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.74,0:04:29.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:29.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and flyin'
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她在唠叨什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's she blabbering about?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.77,0:04:34.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她说陆地生物最强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:34.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She says land creatures are best
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为本来就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only 'cause it's true
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们最会骑马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're best at horseridin'
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.40,0:04:39.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有理毛  赛艇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:39.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and fur stylin' and rowin'
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.47,0:04:41.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,虽说你们游泳比我强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:41.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y'all got us licked in swimmin'
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我们还会剥玉米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but we got corn shuckin'
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,铲干草  养畜禽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and hay bailin' and barn raisin'
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.94,0:04:46.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:46.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and fishin'
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然还有人身攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And name callin' fer sure
Dialogue: 1,0:04:49.67,0:04:50.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有溺水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:50.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And drowning
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了溺水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget drowning
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.65,0:04:55.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真好笑  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:55.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good one, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这辈子你都别想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not on your life, sport
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.71,0:04:59.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我承认
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:04:59.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll admit
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.08,0:05:03.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对于松鼠来说  你确实有点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:03.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got some pretty good moves, for a squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.72,0:05:09.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但你还只是个陆地生物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:09.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you're still just a land creature
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,松鼠想做什么就能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squirrels can do anything they want to
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.63,0:05:16.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定没法一口吃掉双层豪华蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:16.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet you can't eat a Krabby Double Deluxe in one bite
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.65,0:05:22.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:22.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我奇克斯的名号可不是白叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They don't call me Cheeks for nothin'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(444,920)}大 脸 颊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,区区一件小事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that's just one thing
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.35,0:05:31.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:31.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you do this?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.25,0:05:37.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家人全都会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:37.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone in my family can do that
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.31,0:05:41.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:41.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about this, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能出芽生殖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you reproduce by budding?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.90,0:05:44.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:44.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.65,0:05:45.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:45.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.31,0:05:45.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.31,0:05:45.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.79,0:05:46.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:46.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.60,0:05:47.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:47.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.41,0:05:48.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:48.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Most importantly
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.50,0:05:49.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:49.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,can you do this?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.62,0:06:00.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我干嘛要做那堆傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:58.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, what would I want to do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,any of that dumb stuff for anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.97,0:06:02.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,承认吧  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:02.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Admit it, Sandy--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.14,0:06:04.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你做不了我们海底生物能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.14,0:06:04.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can't do anything us sea creatures can do
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实要不是你穿着那身衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In fact, if it wasn't for that suit
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.55,0:06:08.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都不能在这里活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:08.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you couldn't even live down here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.35,0:06:11.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们都不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.35,0:06:11.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.61,0:06:15.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我用不着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:15.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need to
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你们见识
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show y'all
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我用不着这套衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need this suit
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也用不着这个头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I don't need this helmet neither
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海神王保佑她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neptune preserve her
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.77,0:06:33.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她能那样撑多久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:33.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long can she stay like that?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪原来是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy's a girl?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.20,0:06:36.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:36.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确实证明我们错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You sure proved us wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.47,0:06:40.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,陆地生物确实更强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.47,0:06:40.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess land creatures are better
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.80,0:06:45.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过等憋不住要呼吸就弱下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:45.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least, until they need to breathe
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.52,0:06:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上撑不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yep, won't be long now
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.72,0:06:54.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,头晕了没
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:54.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feeling lightheaded yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记得这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember this?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's free
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1222,324)}腌椰菜
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别笑我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop laughin' at me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.61,0:07:23.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:23.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,某些空气笨脑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There was no way some "airhead"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.90,0:07:28.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定赢不过在水里呼吸的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:28.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,was going to win anything against a water breather
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.78,0:07:29.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空气笨脑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:29.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Airhead
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.60,0:07:37.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海底生物最强
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:37.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sea creatures rule
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.57,0:07:40.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:40.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Water
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.42,0:07:44.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们笑就笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:44.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You had your little laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.10,0:07:45.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在该我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:45.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But now it's my turn
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们以为自己都是高手对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y'all think you're such hot stuff, don't ya?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,身上长了鳃就能四处游
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Swimmin' around with your fancy gills 'n such
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你们这群脑子进水的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But none of you wet heads
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.31,0:07:54.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对在我的地盘撑不过一分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:54.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would last a minute on my turf
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.47,0:07:56.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干燥陆地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:56.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dry land
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得戴腌椰菜瓶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do we have to wear pickle jars?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们只要穿自己的衣服上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nope, nothin' but the clothes on your backs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.27,0:08:06.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才一分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:06.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One minute?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.15,0:08:07.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:07.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.37,0:08:08.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:08.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,landy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.15,0:08:22.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们还上不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:22.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, so are you going or not?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.76,0:08:24.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:24.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.28,0:08:24.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:24.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.22,0:08:26.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:26.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.65,0:08:27.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:27.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.64,0:08:28.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.64,0:08:28.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.35,0:08:28.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:28.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.10,0:08:29.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:29.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要赶不上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:30.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,late for
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.77,0:08:31.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,试衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:31.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our fitting
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.35,0:08:34.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该不会是要试穿胆小鸡皮套吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:34.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean for your chicken costumes?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不是胆小鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are not chicken
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.53,0:08:40.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的爆米花
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:40.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My popcorn
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我们不是胆小鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're not chicken
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.82,0:08:44.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上就上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:44.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we'll do it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.26,0:08:48.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:48.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.80,0:08:49.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,任务完成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:49.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mission accomplished
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.90,0:08:53.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  要是不能在陆地待短短一分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:52.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, unless you can stay above water
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for one measly minute
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们比赛就算是弃权
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:55.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you forfeit the contest
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.02,0:08:58.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且证明陆地生物就是比海底生物强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:56.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and prove that land creatures
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,are better than sea creatures
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想得美  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No way, San-day
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.76,0:09:02.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们接受你的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:02.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can take on your challenge
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.71,0:09:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不怕你的破陆地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not afraid of your dumb old land
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.85,0:09:06.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:06.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是海底生物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're sea creatures
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.05,0:09:10.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:10.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.67,0:09:14.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:14.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this is it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.27,0:09:20.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,撑下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:20.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make it last
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:24.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.05,0:09:26.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:26.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:28.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here I go
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.27,0:09:36.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉还行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:36.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't so bad
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:40.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can do this
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  快上来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, come on up
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空气还行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The air is fine
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.74,0:09:46.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.74,0:09:46.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna do it quick and get it over with
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.42,0:09:48.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大炮来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:48.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cannonball
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.16,0:09:51.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我裤子没了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:51.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lost my trunks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.62,0:09:52.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:52.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Pat
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You made it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.72,0:09:56.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:56.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.39,0:09:57.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快上来吧  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:09:57.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on up, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到上面来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.05,0:10:01.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该上岸的都得上岸  章鱼哥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:01.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All ashore that's goin' ashore, Mr. Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去陆地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Land
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.45,0:10:08.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,样子不错  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:08.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lookin' good, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.31,0:10:08.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:08.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.37,0:10:13.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干燥就快让你错过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:13.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're missing all the dry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快来  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.26,0:10:17.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上就上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:17.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll do it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.87,0:10:19.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然而我心不甘情不愿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:19.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I won't like it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:22.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squid
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.75,0:10:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.13,0:10:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here we are
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.57,0:10:30.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还挺简单的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.57,0:10:30.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is pretty easy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可能要在这上面再整一颗石头住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I may keep a second rock up here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.85,0:10:35.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,适应了陆地就能改善不少
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:35.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Once you get your land legs, it's not so bad
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.10,0:10:38.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是陆地和海洋的霸主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:38.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're the masters of land and sea
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.30,0:10:40.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是个土著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.30,0:10:40.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a local
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.23,0:10:42.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是从海底来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.23,0:10:42.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're from underwater
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你认识珊迪奇克斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you know Sandy Cheeks?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.50,0:10:47.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:47.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.20,0:10:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.95,0:10:48.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:48.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, tan my fur
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.45,0:10:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They made it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.55,0:10:52.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好还是去祝贺他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:52.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better go congratulate them
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.06,0:10:54.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:54.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.22,0:10:55.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:55.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们都哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where did those critters get to?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:09.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holy Guacamole
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.77,0:11:12.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许吃我朋友  长翅膀的耗子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:12.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't eat my friends, you rats with wings
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.65,0:11:25.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你救了我们  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:25.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for saving us, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人人各有各的长处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know everyone's best at something
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.52,0:11:31.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但没人能样样精通
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:31.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But no one's best at everything
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉之前让你摘掉头盔  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry I made you take off your helmet, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.86,0:11:36.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉之前让你上干燥的陆地  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:36.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry I made you go up on dry land, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为感到抱歉欢呼三声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three cheers for feeling sorry for ourselves
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.90,0:11:40.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:40.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hip-hip
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:42.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.08,0:11:42.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:42.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hip-hip
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.80,0:11:44.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:44.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.22,0:11:44.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:44.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hip-hip
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hooray
