Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(716,316)}裤头村动物园             牡蛎体育场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(866,750)}年度免费节
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.70,0:12:02.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:02.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah
Dialogue: 1,0:12:02.57,0:12:04.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村动物园
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:04.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Bikini Bottom Zoo
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.16,0:12:06.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在举行年度免费节
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:06.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is having its annual free day
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.02,0:12:08.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费气球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:08.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Free balloons
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.60,0:12:11.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:11.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,free drinks
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免费灯泡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,free light bulbs?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.12,0:12:18.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家早上好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:18.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Top 'o the mornin', boys
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.75,0:12:21.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一站
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:21.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Next stop
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.94,0:12:22.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼品店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:22.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,gift shop
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:25.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(366,282)}礼品店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:25.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(916,324)}牡蛎体育场
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:24.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There it is--
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.15,0:12:25.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牡蛎体育场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:25.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oyster Stadium
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.91,0:12:26.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那边不仅仅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:26.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not only do they have
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.87,0:12:29.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圈养着最大的牡蛎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:29.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the largest oyster held in captivity
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.07,0:12:30.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还会演杂技
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:30.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it also does tricks
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.71,0:12:35.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牡蛎把大珍珠吐到了一百英尺高
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:35.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He spits a giant pearl 100 feet in the air
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宛如一颗炮弹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like a cannon ball
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我们还闲逛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why are we hanging around
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看你瞎模仿干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,watching a cheap imitation?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.74,0:12:45.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,直接过去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:45.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get over there
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.03,0:12:50.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是我们一生中最棒的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:50.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the greatest day of our lives
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.02,0:13:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是我们一生中最棒的一天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:13:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the greatest day of our lives?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.15,0:13:02.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:02.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boring
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.60,0:13:06.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:06.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.87,0:13:07.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要来看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:07.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we came to see
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.85,0:13:10.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吐到一百英尺高的大珍珠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:10.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pearls 100 feet in the air
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.12,0:13:10.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:10.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来学牡蛎叫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:12.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll try my oyster call
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.02,0:13:23.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:23.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm outta here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.42,0:13:25.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你带我白来一场  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:25.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for nothin', SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on
Dialogue: 1,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶快醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wake up already
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.79,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,944)}海花生
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好像成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think it's working
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.79,0:13:45.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  它醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:45.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, it's waking up
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  我错过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, did I miss it?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.47,0:13:49.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没  杂技才刚要开始演
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:49.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, the show's about to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:55.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(552,446)}大蚌
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.45,0:13:58.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大蚌怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:58.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Clamu?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小妹冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Easy, girl
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我小乔  还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's me, Joe, remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.78,0:14:11.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这场杂技才好看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:11.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, this is a show
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.03,0:14:12.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动物园游客请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:12.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attention, zoo patrons
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.91,0:14:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巨型牡蛎大蚌正在发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Clamu The Giant Oyster is on an emotional rampage
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请尖叫并绕圈跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please scream and run around in circles
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.71,0:14:21.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢大家光临
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:21.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.47,0:14:26.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们最好立刻离开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.47,0:14:26.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You boys better get out of this area, pronto
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.97,0:14:28.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最危险的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:28.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's nothing more dangerous
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.56,0:14:30.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当属这只精神失常的大牡蛎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:30.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than an emotionally disturbed oyster
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.72,0:14:34.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,造成这场悲剧的应该不是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:32.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You didn't do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:34.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that might have caused this tragedy, did you?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.97,0:14:36.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:36.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.92,0:14:39.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有大浑球才会害温和的大牡蛎生气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:39.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only a jerk would upset a gentle giant
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.97,0:14:41.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:41.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.12,0:14:42.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.12,0:14:42.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:53.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(858,370)}裤头村动物园
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.09,0:14:50.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是让我看到那位害大蚌生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:50.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man, if I ever see the guy who upset Clamu
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.61,0:14:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有好几个备选的词来骂他  比如
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd have a few choice words for him, like
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.00,0:14:54.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:54.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"you"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.68,0:14:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.72,0:14:56.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:56.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"are"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.47,0:14:57.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:57.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.51,0:14:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"a jerk"
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.66,0:15:01.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确定没看到什么可疑的迹象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:01.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you didn't see anything suspicious?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都说没看到了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I already said I didn't, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来一起调查这场罪案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's investigate this crime
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住作案的坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:09.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and catch the lowlife who's responsible
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.50,0:15:10.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:10.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give it a rest, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.92,0:15:13.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就没罪案留给你查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.92,0:15:13.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's no crime to investigate
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now go home
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笨蛋派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stupid Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.50,0:15:19.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才没犯什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:19.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还烦什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What am I getting so worked up about?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.47,0:15:24.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等到明天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:24.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that by tomorrow
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.91,0:15:27.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这场大乱肯定会变成笑谈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:27.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this whole ugly mess will be a funny memory
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.96,0:15:29.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚的头条新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:29.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our top story tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.77,0:15:32.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巨型牡蛎遭受心理创伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:32.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,giant oyster has its feelings hurt
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.28,0:15:34.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现场唯一的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:34.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The only clue that could be found
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.28,0:15:35.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有这一颗花生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:35.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,was this lone peanut
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家可以听到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:37.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And as you can hear
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.42,0:15:41.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牡蛎仍在凄惨地哭泣着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:41.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the oyster continues to emit its horrible cry
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.22,0:15:45.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哭声之强  乃至全世界都能听到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:45.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A cry so powerful, it can be heard around the world
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.00,0:15:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这哭声不但能打破音障
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A cry that not only breaks the sound barrier
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.92,0:15:51.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还伤了广大居民们的心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:51.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it breaks the hearts of our citizens
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.26,0:15:55.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是怎样残暴淡漠又邪恶的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:55.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What kind of cruel careless, evil person
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.76,0:16:00.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会存心激怒海底最为温和的生物之一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would deliberately upset
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:00.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one of Neptune's most gentle creatures?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:04.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.75,0:16:06.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我哪知道牡蛎的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:06.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How would I know anything about the oyster?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.47,0:16:08.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,狡辩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:08.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Defensive?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才没狡辩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not being defensive
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:10.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么鬼东西  问答游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this, 20 questions or something?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,情况有点失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is getting a little out of hand
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才扔了颗花生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I did was throw a peanut
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.02,0:16:20.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又没故意要惹哭牡蛎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:20.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to make the oyster cry
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.12,0:16:23.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是想看它表演杂技
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:23.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see it perform spectacular stunts
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下大家都要恨我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone's going to hate me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.28,0:16:28.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我  我需要建议
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:28.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, I need some advice
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, let's see now
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.47,0:16:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁会不论我做了什么事都不恨我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who could never hate me no matter what I do?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.13,0:16:34.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:34.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.12,0:16:35.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:35.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.68,0:16:36.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:36.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.52,0:16:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你非得这么大声敲门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you have to knock so loudly?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.82,0:16:41.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:41.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, neighbor
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.63,0:16:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那头大蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That overgrown clam
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害我头疼死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is giving me a headache
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连午后美容觉都不让我睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't even take my afternoon beauty nap
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说到了那头老牡蛎  挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Funny thing you should mention that old oyster
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.61,0:16:52.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:52.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because I
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.05,0:16:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,was kind wondering, um
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.06,0:17:02.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像认得惹了牡蛎的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:59.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's say I know this guy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:02.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who may have something to do with the oyster
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你认识犯事的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:04.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know the guy who did it?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.60,0:17:06.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:06.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is great
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.72,0:17:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我和你能让他就地正法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You and I can go turn him in
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后我就能好好睡美容觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And then I'll get so much sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再然后就帅起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:11.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be gorgeous
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.65,0:17:12.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其实我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:12.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, I
Dialogue: 1,0:17:12.28,0:17:14.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚刚那是假设
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:14.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just talking hypothetically
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.05,0:17:15.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不认识真凶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:15.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean you don't know who did it?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, um
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.57,0:17:17.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:17.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.15,0:17:18.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:18.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.60,0:17:20.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:20.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:22.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.49,0:17:24.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你今天的那天在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:24.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where were you on the day of today?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.32,0:17:26.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许耍我  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:26.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't play games with me, mister
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.80,0:17:28.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:28.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.60,0:17:29.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.60,0:17:29.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.52,0:17:33.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在继续大蚌案的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:31.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just continuing my investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of the great Clamu Caper
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.63,0:17:36.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:36.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you found out anything?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:37.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.40,0:17:38.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:38.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.57,0:17:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过这粒沙子感觉十分可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But this grain of sand looks pretty suspicious
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这颗石头也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and so does this rock
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.40,0:17:49.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还有几个问题想问这棵草
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I've got a few questions
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:49.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for this little piece of grass
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.28,0:17:51.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放心  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:51.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.92,0:17:53.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星来破案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:53.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's on the case
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.34,0:17:56.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真相要公诸于世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:56.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The truth will be revealed
Dialogue: 1,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去找珊迪  她知道该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd better go see Sandy, she'll know what to do
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.78,0:18:02.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个可怜的小家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That poor, poor critter
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.75,0:18:06.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是怎样淡漠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:06.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What kind of inconsiderate person
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.97,0:18:09.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,居然会如此惹怒这样一只温和的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:09.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would upset such a gentle creature?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.66,0:18:11.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就是我想跟你说的事  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:11.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's kind of what I wanted to talk to you about, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.08,0:18:16.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等我找到严重伤害牡蛎的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:16.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, when I find out who caused that oyster so much pain
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.72,0:18:19.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得让他再也耍不了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:19.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more jiggery pokery
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.74,0:18:20.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,298)}裤头村黄页
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.29,0:18:24.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你刚刚想跟我说什么  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:24.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, what was it you wanted to talk about, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.17,0:18:30.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你怎么在抽搐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:30.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, how come you're all twitchy like that?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.17,0:18:30.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抽搐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:30.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Twitchy?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:30.98,0:18:31.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抽搐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:31.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Twitchy?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁抽搐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's twitchy?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才没抽搐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:34.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not twitchy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.74,0:18:35.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:35.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.39,0:18:36.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:36.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to um
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去剪头发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,go get my hair cut
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝没头发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob doesn't have hair
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会还真有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or does he?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:50.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.83,0:18:56.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有线索都汇聚在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.83,0:18:56.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All of the clues are coming together
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.23,0:19:00.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟着这些脚印到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:19:00.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I followed these footprints right to this exact spot
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后  就是在你站的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and then, right where you're standing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发现了这袋花生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found this bag of peanuts
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.53,0:19:09.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就快侦破这起罪案了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.53,0:19:09.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm so close to solving this crime
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.62,0:19:12.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都快尝得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:12.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can almost taste it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.06,0:19:17.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  打击犯罪让我饿坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:17.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, crime-fighting sure makes me hungry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这根黄色冰棍刚好能解馋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:19.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and this yellow popsicle hits the spot
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.80,0:19:20.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:20.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.81,0:19:21.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你破案好运  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:21.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,good luck with all that, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.97,0:19:22.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:22.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等会见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll see you later
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.06,0:19:25.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:25.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open up
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.43,0:19:27.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里是警察
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:27.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the police
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just a second
Dialogue: 1,0:19:30.57,0:19:32.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是海绵宝宝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:32.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you SpongeBob SquarePants?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.73,0:19:34.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:34.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Y-y-yes?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把眼球安回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Put those eyeballs back in your head, son
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们有几个问题要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got a few questions for you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.28,0:19:42.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牡蛎事件发生那天  你在动物园吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:42.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Were you at the zoo on the day of the oyster incident?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.86,0:19:45.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:45.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是否参与了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you, or did you not take part
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.01,0:19:49.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动物园的各项游乐活动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:49.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in various activities of zoo-time merriment?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.81,0:19:50.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:50.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你认得这颗花生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And are you familiar with this peanut?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:53.21,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(362,728)}物证{\fnArial}A
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.83,0:19:54.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:54.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just one more question
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.80,0:19:59.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是否先前在牡蛎窝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:59.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it true that you were at the oyster's lair
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.89,0:20:02.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟派大星先生在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:02.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with a Mr. Patrick Star?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:03.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.62,0:20:04.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.62,0:20:04.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.25,0:20:05.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:05.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's true
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.65,0:20:07.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:07.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all true
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.98,0:20:09.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,游乐活动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:09.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The merriment
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.55,0:20:10.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,花生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:10.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the peanut
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.09,0:20:12.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:12.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们想了解的就这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's all we need to know, son
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.40,0:20:15.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对他立案
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:15.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's book him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们也太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys are good
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.67,0:20:22.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最不会怀疑的人就是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:22.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the last person I would have suspected
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.34,0:20:25.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我一直都在找我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:25.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I was looking for me all the time
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.25,0:20:26.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好完美的犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:26.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect crime
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.82,0:20:27.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:27.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.95,0:20:30.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟法官说去吧  小粉红
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.95,0:20:30.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,tell it to the judge, pinky
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.05,0:20:31.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:31.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.20,0:20:33.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星对监狱过敏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:33.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's too sensitive for the big house
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:33.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(954,842)}警察
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  停车
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.10,0:20:38.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才是你们要抓的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:38.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the one you want
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才是罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am the criminal
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:43.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(398,874)}牡蛎体育场
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.56,0:20:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家一起朝他扔花生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, everybody, let's throw peanuts at him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.55,0:20:53.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看他会作何感想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:53.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and see how he likes it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.40,0:20:57.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是我罪有应得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:20:57.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I get what I deserve
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.20,0:21:04.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:04.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先别扔花生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold your peanuts
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:08.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick Star is innocent
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.49,0:21:11.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我过来这里要揭露真相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:11.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have come here to reveal the truth
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.27,0:21:14.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人人都说只要诚实相待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:14.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They say that truth and honesty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.55,0:21:17.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方能换取信任与原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:17.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will be rewarded with trust and forgiveness
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.61,0:21:19.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在此向大家坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:19.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm here to lay my cards on the table
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.12,0:21:23.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以此砍去我生命之树上的欺瞒枝杈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:23.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to trim the branches of deception from the tree of life
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.20,0:21:27.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刮去我真相之脸上的邋遢鬓角
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:25.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to shave away the unkempt sideburns
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:27.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the face of truth
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.30,0:21:27.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:27.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.48,0:21:30.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有话快说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:30.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just get on with it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.47,0:21:32.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我扔的花生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:32.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am the one who threw the peanut
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.14,0:21:35.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我明白我的所作所为铸成了大错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:35.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know now that what I have done is wrong
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.21,0:21:37.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要向大家说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.21,0:21:37.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and so I say
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.55,0:21:40.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  巨型杂技牡蛎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:40.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am sorry, giant performing oyster
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.25,0:21:42.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:42.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am sorry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.03,0:21:45.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  裤头村居民们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:45.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am sorry, citizens of Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.70,0:21:50.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家朝他们两个扔花生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:50.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's throw peanuts at both of 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.41,0:21:53.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:53.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.39,0:21:55.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才是真正的罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:55.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's the real criminal
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.67,0:21:58.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Top of the morning
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.51,0:22:00.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.51,0:22:00.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.67,0:22:02.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:02.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew it
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.75,0:22:07.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板偷了牡蛎一样非常重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs has stolen a very important item
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:07.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the oyster
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.06,0:22:09.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.06,0:22:09.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behold
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.09,0:22:12.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.09,0:22:12.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.25,0:22:14.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:14.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behold
Dialogue: 1,0:22:14.64,0:22:16.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牡蛎的珍珠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:16.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The oyster's pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.62,0:22:20.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还给你  小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.62,0:22:20.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, girl
Dialogue: 1,0:22:34.18,0:22:35.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.18,0:22:35.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mama
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.22,0:22:36.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:36.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mama
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.42,0:22:38.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍的妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:38.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother of pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.05,0:22:39.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那只牡蛎是位母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.05,0:22:39.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The oyster's a mother
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.67,0:22:41.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且珍珠也不是珍珠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:41.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And that pearl's no pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.62,0:22:42.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而是颗卵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.62,0:22:42.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's an egg
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.84,0:22:44.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:44.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mama
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.10,0:22:45.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.10,0:22:45.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mama
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.97,0:22:58.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可今天是免费节
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:22:58.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's free day
